Last but not least, good practice in
data documentation and citation can

45
00:03:17,625 --> 00:03:23,230
contribute to reaching a better standard
of reproducibility of research.

46
00:03:23,230 --> 00:03:27,510
Reproducibility is a fundamental
principle of the scientific method.

